\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 
\series bold
Ritorno
\series default
: 
\begin_inset Formula $\teorema{a_{1}\wedge}...\wedge a_{n}\implies(a\implies b)$
\end_inset

, basta portare 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 tra le 
\begin_inset Formula $ $
\end_inset

and.
 
